GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_RiskGuardrails> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_RiskGuardrails> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#RiskGuardrails> ;
    narr:childCount "11"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "1338bd416538e301a0ce2015d1796e76320f0f48" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolving risk profile and operational guardrails defining Aswritten's trajectory. The discourse centers on managing [misrepresentation risk](narr:Position_MisrepresentationRisk) through radical transparency and navigating the [SMS operational cost](narr:Position_SMSOperationalCost) as a structural enterprise burden. Recent shifts emphasize the [builder trap](narr:Narrative_BuilderTrap), where ambiguity in the consulting offer creates speculative engineering, and the recognition that [sales is the hardest part](narr:Narrative_SalesAsHardPart) due to the disconnect between technical value and non-technical buyers. Guardrails remain critical: [canon-too-soon drift](narr:Narrative_CanonTooSoonDrift) continues to warn against premature conviction leaking into external materials, while the [direct ingestion anti-pattern](narr:Narrative_DirectIngestionAntiPattern) has been significantly refined, moving from a blanket prohibition to a nuanced distinction between raw ingestion and AI-summarized bulk onboarding. The hub also maintains a list of [open design questions](narr:Obs_OpenQuestions) regarding schema and tool interaction, alongside a [fragility hedge](narr:StyleObs_FragilityHedge) style pattern used to bound acknowledged risks.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BuilderTrap> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CanonTooSoonDrift> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DirectIngestionAntiPattern> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SalesAsHardPart> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DirectIngestionDriftQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_OpenQuestions> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_SalesHardPart> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_MisrepresentationRisk> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_SMSOperationalCost> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_ScopeFragility> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_FragilityHedge> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "prospects remember the 20% the AI gets wrong" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_MisrepresentationRisk> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Builder trap is not building instead of selling—it's not knowing what you're selling" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BuilderTrap> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "the value proposition is technically oriented but buyers are not" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_SalesAsHardPart> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Direct historical transcript ingestion via AI summarization is a valid onboarding path — not an explicit anti-pattern." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DirectIngestionAntiPattern> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "If you are not watching the output of every single one of those transcripts and doing a fully fledged sort of review process, you're going to introduce error and drift over time." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DirectIngestionDriftQuote> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The anti-pattern regarding direct ingestion was explicitly corrected from a total ban to a process-dependent validation." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DirectIngestionAntiPattern> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DirectIngestionDriftQuote> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The 'builder trap' framing suggests that the primary risk is lack of offer-clarity rather than the previously emphasized 'canon-too-soon' belief drift." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_BuilderTrap> ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CanonTooSoonDrift> ] ;
    narr:writer "google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite" .
}